One contract is significantly older than the other, they both use the same token name and meta data.

ethfinance.live is talking to this contract.

<https://bscscan.com/address/0xAE6d1bf05154E5F14646a588b8f43D42a40705F3#code>

While ethfinance.online is talking to this contract.

<https://bscscan.com/address/0x18c6c7919b1de01846758f39b90c3a35b32178a3#code>

